@startuml infrastructure-overview

title Infrastructure Overview — Docker Compose Components

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 8

actor       "Developer / User"     as user
participant "Angular"              as spa    #LightGray
participant "jwt-demo :8081"       as app    #LightBlue
participant "Keycloak :8080"       as kc     #LightGreen
database    "postgres-app :5433"   as dbapp  #LightYellow
database    "postgres :5432"       as dbkc   #LightYellow
participant "otel-collector :4318" as otel   #Plum
participant "Tempo :3200"          as tempo  #Pink
participant "Loki :3100"           as loki   #Pink
participant "Prometheus :9090"     as prom   #Orange
participant "Grafana :3000"        as graf   #LightCoral

== Startup ==

kc   -> dbkc  : stores realm, users, sessions
app  -> dbapp : Flyway runs pending migrations
app  -> kc    : reads OIDC config (introspection URL)

== Login Request ==

user -> spa   : enters credentials
spa  -> app   : POST /api/auth/login
app  -> kc    : POST /token (grant_type=password)
kc   -> dbkc  : validates user
dbkc --> kc   : user found
kc   --> app  : { access_token, refresh_token }
app  --> spa  : AT in body + RT in Set-Cookie

== Authenticated Request ==

spa  -> app   : GET /api/clients\nAuthorization: Bearer <AT>
app  -> kc    : POST /introspect (validates AT)
kc   --> app  : { active: true, roles, sub }
app  -> dbapp : query business data
dbapp --> app : result
app  --> spa  : 200 OK

== Observability (async, every request) ==

app  -> otel  : traces + logs (OTLP HTTP :4318)
otel -> tempo : forwards traces
otel -> loki  : forwards logs

prom -> app   : scrapes GET /actuator/prometheus\n(metrics pull every 15s)

== Grafana Dashboard ==

user -> graf  : opens dashboard :3000
graf -> prom  : queries metrics (PromQL)
graf -> loki  : queries logs (LogQL)
graf -> tempo : queries traces (TraceQL)
graf --> user : unified view\n(metrics + logs + traces correlated by traceId)

@enduml
